data.description: Whether you're looking to downsize or looking for a one level home, 1416 Napier may be the place for you.  Newer laminate floors and even two bedrooms with original hardwood floors, a newer metal roof and freshly painted walls await the new owners.   There's a large, level backyard, partially fenced with plenty of room for a pool or entertainment area.  You could spend the holidays in a new home this year! Call or text your local real estate agent for a showing!
